query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.favorite_count >= 0 AND q.favorite_count <= 10000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('android-5.0-lollipop',
'augmented-reality',
'conditional-statements',
'drawing',
'instagram',
'max',
'seaborn',
'sharedpreferences',
'slider',
'styles',
'wmi');
